# Aqarify Landing Page Revamp Rules

## Goal

Revamp the tenant-facing landing page into a premium, conversion-focused Aqarify real-estate experience.

This is NOT the SaaS marketing homepage.
This is the customer-facing property landing page for each real-estate tenant/developer.

Primary user:
- Property buyer or renter
- Visitor comparing projects/units
- Customer who may reserve, join waitlist, schedule visit, or contact sales

Business goal:
- Increase browse clicks
- Increase unit reservations
- Increase schedule-visit/contact intent
- Increase trust in the tenant/developer

